Package com.j256.ormlite.stmt.query

Interface Summary
Clause Internal marker class for query clauses.
NeedsFutureClause Internal interface which defines a clause that consumes a future clause.
 

Class Summary
And Internal class that handles the AND sql operation which takes two Clause parts.
Between Internal class handling the SQL 'between' query part.
Eq Internal class handling the SQL '=' comparison query part.
Exists Internal class handling the SQL 'EXISTS' query part.
Ge Internal class handling the SQL '>=' comparison query part.
Gt Internal class handling the SQL '>' comparison query part.
In Internal class handling the SQL 'in' query part.
InSubQuery Internal class handling the SQL 'in' query part.
IsNotNull Internal class handling the SQL 'IS NOT NULL' comparison query part.
IsNull Internal class handling the SQL 'IS NULL' comparison query part.
Le Internal class handling the SQL '<=' comparison query part.
Like Internal class handling the SQL 'like' comparison query part.
Lt Internal class handling the SQL '<' comparison query part.
Ne Internal class handling the SQL '<>' comparison query part.
Not Internal class handling the SQL 'NOT' boolean comparison operation.
Or Internal class handling the SQL 'OR' operation which takes two Clause parts.
OrderBy Internal class handling the SQL 'ORDER BY' operation.
Raw Raw part of the where to just stick in a string in the middle of the WHERE.
SetExpression Internal class handling the SQL SET part used by UPDATE statements.
SetValue Internal class handling the SQL SET part used by UPDATE statements.
